      </li>
      <li xml:id="exer_sec11-2">
        <p>
          Identify the hypothesis and the conclusion for each of the following conditional statements.
          <ol>
            <li>
              <p>
                If <m>n</m> is a prime number,
                then <m>n^2</m> has three positive factors.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                If <m>a</m> is an irrational number and <m>b</m> is an irrational number,
