      </li>
      <li xml:id="exer_sec11-3">
        <p>
          Determine whether each of the following conditional statements is true or false.
          <ol>
            <li>
              <p>
                If <m>10 \lt 7</m>, then <m>3 = 4</m>.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                If <m>7 \lt 10</m>, then <m>3 = 4</m>.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                If <m>10 \lt 7</m>, then <m>3 + 5 = 8</m>.
              </p>
            </li>
